      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FANCY BELLA (3) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (30.21) in a Grade 5 at Wentworth Park. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Can make amends. SQUARE UP (4) could manage only third at this track last time but turned heads when clocking a superb 29.69 over 520m at Wentworth Park three starts ago. Expected to feature on best figures. AUSSIE BLEND (8) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (22.91) at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Has ability and can atone. MISS GLAMOURPUSS (2) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished second last time (22.49) at Richmond. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors.",
